\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4304,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/05\/recommendation-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":36185,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Witr: Recommendation to perform witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Witr prayer is a duty upon every Muslim. Whoever likes to pray it with five cycles, let him do so. Whoever likes to pray it with three cycles, let him do so. Whoever likes to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/pray-witr-before-morning\/","url_meta":{"origin":36185,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Pray Witr before morning comes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPerform Witr prayer before the morning.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 754 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u0650\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0623\u06